{"tid":1587591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論]發揮創意，唔同程度既自衛還擊!!","createTime":"2019-09-22T12:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T14:02:37.000Z","uid":300294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9671733ab1add0f69d7e6157bf77d2a90d7fb225","tid":1587591,"uid":300294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:55:42.000Z","msg":"呢兩日討論自衛還擊個程度，好似只係偏向討論某幾件事，就係元朗沙田應唔應該打破壞連儂牆既人 (亦都有人話佢地有郁手先)。<br />\n其實更廣泛既，更值得引申討論既係 對面唔同武力既程度，我地應該有咩相應既行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲記得機場傅國豪事件後，當日都係討論係咪太激。<br />\n之後818夜晚，有個中國籍男子出黎搞事。但係當晚手足係無打佢，就咁同佢影幾張相，番黎改下圖玩下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/68703376_378571969473519_6015360461237649408_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_eui2=AeG1DIJShP8zYsePBYEm9AoHmxEE3eMwHjsZmog1eDHDNNUQGlRag-hjtCc2FNVfaWr5DIi_a67UuUG1teFtTV6PUsF8NNipPOcJKWKXbCYagw&amp;_nc_oc=AQlQo892JFxKoG7siRUN4Dv__Y9aYSqs4mIsMigMZQgxHrclEaPD-Fq00ZPkOIqlI_E&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=7da5f36ace1449c3b6dde6f6318ec16a&amp;oe=5DFA3792\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F68703376_378571969473519_6015360461237649408_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_eui2%3DAeG1DIJShP8zYsePBYEm9AoHmxEE3eMwHjsZmog1eDHDNNUQGlRag-hjtCc2FNVfaWr5DIi_a67UuUG1teFtTV6PUsF8NNipPOcJKWKXbCYagw%26_nc_oc%3DAQlQo892JFxKoG7siRUN4Dv__Y9aYSqs4mIsMigMZQgxHrclEaPD-Fq00ZPkOIqlI_E%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D7da5f36ace1449c3b6dde6f6318ec16a%26oe%3D5DFA3792&h=82dc4f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我地有無可能有其他方法去應對 對方不同既行動? 唔限死於打同唔打。<br />\n對面放嘴炮既，可以唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n對面撕文宣，會否考慮用番818個方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n佢郁手先既，咁好遺憾，人人都要保障自己安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n上述只係我個人既愚見，我亦都唔係割席。只係覺得打同唔打中間仲有好大空間。<br />\n大家可以發揮下創意，諗下用咩唔同既行動，去回應番對面。<br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1607e6eade9a76b9d0f68901c68c51b7025bef4","tid":1587591,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5b602f9480d8574b8d41a525bea2ca0076c9938","tid":1587591,"uid":300294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37aff2ce6f1aa4986a779ce7d491f9789ddd80d2","tid":1587591,"uid":300294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:57:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7930b2386e36d2fc6c3dff79c6f9a3b377def5a9","tid":1587591,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:00:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"cacf1882b08b221be8b1e18fa7be6ea282a75964","tid":1587591,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"支持"}]}